---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Tým Domova Turovice – lidé, kteří se starají o vaše blízké"
  description="Poznejte pečovatele, sestry a sociální pracovníky Domova Turovice. Tým s praxí, který o vaše blízké pečuje 24 hodin denně. Zjistěte více."
>

<style>
/* ══ HERO ══ */
.tym-hero {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--clr-primary) 0%, #5a2a30 100%);
  color: #fff;
  padding: 72px 0 60px;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.tym-hero::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  width: 420px; height: 420px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
  top: -120px; right: -80px;
  pointer-events: none;
}
.tym-hero::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  width: 260px; height: 260px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
  bottom: -80px; left: -60px;
  pointer-events: none;
}
.tym-hero-inner {
  max-width: var(--container);
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 0 24px;
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
}
.tym-hero-kicker {
  display: inline-block;
  font-family: var(--ff-body);
  font-size: var(--font-size-label);
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: .12em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.70);
  margin-bottom: 18px;
}
.tym-hero h1 {
  font-family: var(--ff-head);
  font-size: clamp(2.1rem, 4.5vw, 3.2rem);
  font-weight: 700;
  color: #fff;
  line-height: 1.15;
  margin: 0 0 20px;
}
.tym-hero h1 em {
  font-style: italic;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.88);
}
.tym-hero-perex {
  font-family: var(--ff-body);
  font-size: 1.15rem;
  line-height: 1.65;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.86);
  max-width: 580px;
  margin: 0 0 28px;
}
.hero-btn-wrap {
  display: flex;
  gap: 12px;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}
.hero-btn-primary {
  display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 9px;
  background: #fff; color: var(--clr-primary);
  border: 2px solid #fff;
  font-family: var(--ff-body); font-size: var(--font-size-ui); font-weight: 700;
  padding: 14px 28px; border-radius: var(--radius-btn);
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: background .2s, color .2s, border-color .2s;
}
.hero-btn-primary:hover { background: transparent; color: #fff; border-color: #fff; }
.hero-btn-secondary {
  display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 9px;
  background: transparent; color: #fff;
  border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.65);
  font-family: var(--ff-body); font-size: var(--font-size-ui); font-weight: 600;
  padding: 14px 28px; border-radius: var(--radius-btn);
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: background .2s, border-color .2s;
}
.hero-btn-secondary:hover { border-color: #fff; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.12); }
@media(max-width:480px) {
  .hero-btn-wrap { flex-direction: column; }
  .hero-btn-primary, .hero-btn-secondary { justify-content: center; }
}

/* ══ STAT STRIP ══ */
.stat-strip {
  background: var(--clr-surface);
  padding: 44px 0;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--clr-border);
}
.stat-strip-inner {
  max-width: var(--container);
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 0 24px;
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 24px;
  text-align: center;
}
.stat-item-num {
  font-family: var(--ff-head);
  font-size: 2.6rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--clr-primary);
  line-height: 1.1;
  display: block;
}
.stat-item-label {
  font-family: var(--ff-body);
  font-size: var(--font-size-base);
  color: var(--clr-text-muted);
  line-height: 1.5;
  display: block;
  margin-top: 6px;
}
@media(max-width:600px) {
  .stat-strip-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 32px; }
}

/* ══ OBECNÉ SEKCE ══ */
.container {
  max-width: var(--container);
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 0 24px;
}
.section-label {
  display: block;
  text-align: center;
  font-family: var(--ff-body);
  font-size: var(--font-size-label);
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: .12em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--clr-primary);
  margin-bottom: 14px;
}
.section-intro {
  text-align: center;
  max-width: 680px;
  margin: 0 auto 52px;
}
.section-intro h2 {
  font-family: var(--ff-head);
  font-size: var(--font-size-h2);
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--clr-primary);
  line-height: 1.20;
  margin: 0 0 14px;
}
.section-intro p {
  font-family: var(--ff-body);
  font-size: var(--font-size-base);
  color: var(--clr-text-body);
  line-height: 1.70;
}
@media(max-width:768px) {
  .section-intro h2 { font-size: var(--font-size-h2-mob); }
}

/* ══ VEDENÍ ══ */
.vedeni-section {
  padding: 88px 0;
  background: var(--clr-bg);
}
.vedeni-card {
  max-width: 860px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  background: #fff;
  border-radius: var(--radius-card);
  box-shadow: var(--shadow-card);
  border-top: 3px solid var(--clr-primary);
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 240px 1fr;
  gap: 0;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.vedeni-photo {
  background: var(--clr-surface);
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  padding: 40px 24px;
  gap: 16px;
  border-right: 1px solid var(--clr-border);
}
.vedeni-photo-placeholder {
  width: 160px; height: 200px;
  border-radius: 12px;
  background: var(--clr-border);
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  gap: 10px;
  color: var(--clr-text-muted);
  font-family: var(--ff-body);
  font-size: 12px;
  text-align: center;
  padding: 12px;
}
.vedeni-photo-placeholder svg {
  width: 48px; height: 48px;
  stroke: var(--clr-text-muted);
  fill: none;
  stroke-width: 1.5;
  stroke-linecap: round;
  stroke-linejoin: round;
}
.vedeni-badge {
  background: var(--clr-primary);
  color: #fff;
  font-family: var(--ff-body);
  font-size: 11px;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: .06em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  padding: 6px 14px;
  border-radius: 20px;
  text-align: center;
}
.vedeni-content {
  padding: 40px 44px;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  justify-content: center;
  gap: 16px;
}
.vedeni-role {
  font-family: var(--ff-body);
  font-size: var(--font-size-label);
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: .10em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--clr-primary);
}
.vedeni-content h3 {
  font-family: var(--ff-head);
  font-size: 1.6rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--clr-text-dark);
  margin: 0;
  line-height: 1.25;
}
.vedeni-content p {
  font-family: var(--ff-body);
  font-size: var(--font-size-base);
  color: var(--clr-text-body);
  line-height: 1.70;
  margin: 0;
}
.vedeni-cert-list {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 8px;
  margin: 4px 0 0;
  padding: 0;
  list-style: none;
}
.vedeni-cert-list li {
  font-family: var(--ff-body);
  font-size: 13px;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--clr-primary);
  background: var(--clr-primary-soft);
  padding: 4px 12px;
  border-radius: 20px;
}
.vedeni-link {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 6px;
  font-family: var(--ff-body);
  font-size: var(--font-size-base);
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--clr-primary);
  text-decoration: none;
  margin-top: 4px;
  transition: gap .18s;
}
.vedeni-link:hover { gap: 10px; }
.vedeni-link svg { width: 16px; height: 16px; stroke: currentColor; fill: none; stroke-width: 2; stroke-linecap: round; stroke-linejoin: round; }
@media(max-width:768px) {
  .vedeni-card { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .vedeni-photo { border-right: none; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--clr-border); padding: 32px 24px; flex-direction: row; justify-content: flex-start; }
  .vedeni-photo-placeholder { width: 100px; height: 120px; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .vedeni-content { padding: 28px 24px; }
}

/* ══ TÝM KARTY ══ */
.tym-section {
  padding: 88px 0;
}
.tym-section--surface { background: var(--clr-surface); }
.tym-section--bg { background: var(--clr-bg); }
.tym-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 24px;
}
.tym-grid--4 { grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); }
.tym-grid--2 { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
.tym-card {
  background: #fff;
  border-radius: var(--radius-card);
  box-shadow: var(--shadow-card);
  border-top: 3px solid var(--clr-primary);
  overflow: hidden;
  transition: box-shadow .22s, transform .22s;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
}
.tym-card:hover {
  box-shadow: var(--shadow-hover);
  transform: translateY(-4px);
}
.tym-card-photo {
  width: 100%;
  aspect-ratio: 4/3;
  background: var(--clr-surface);
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  gap: 10px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--clr-border);
}
.tym-card-photo svg {
  width: 48px; height: 48px;
  stroke: var(--clr-text-muted);
  fill: none;
  stroke-width: 1.5;
  stroke-linecap: round;
  stroke-linejoin: round;
  opacity: 0.6;
}
.tym-card-photo-label {
  font-family: var(--ff-body);
  font-size: 12px;
  color: var(--clr-text-muted);
  text-align: center;
  padding: 0 12px;
}
.tym-card-body {
  padding: 24px 24px 28px;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 8px;
  flex: 1;
}
.tym-card-role {
  font-family: var(--ff-body);
  font-size: 11px;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: .10em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--clr-primary);
}
.tym-card-name {
  font-family: var(--ff-head);
  font-size: var(--font-size-subhead);
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--clr-text-dark);
  line-height: 1.30;
  margin: 0;
}
.tym-card-desc {
  font-family: var(--ff-body);
  font-size: var(--font-size-base);
  color: var(--clr-text-body);
  line-height: 1.65;
  margin: 4px 0 0;
  flex: 1;
}
@media(max-width:1024px) {
  .tym-grid--4 { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
  .tym-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
}
@media(max-width:600px) {
  .tym-grid, .tym-grid--4, .tym-grid--2 { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
}

/* ══ PODPŮRNÝ TÝM – 3 jednoduché karty ══ */
.support-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 24px;
}
.support-card {
  background: #fff;
  border-radius: var(--radius-card);
  box-shadow: var(--shadow-card);
  padding: 32px 28px;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 12px;
  border-top: 3px solid var(--clr-border);
  transition: box-shadow .22s, transform .22s, border-top-color .22s;
}
.support-card:hover {
  box-shadow: var(--shadow-hover);
  transform: translateY(-4px);
  border-top-color: var(--clr-primary);
}
.support-card-icon {
  width: 44px; height: 44px;
  background: var(--clr-primary-soft);
  border-radius: 10px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}
.support-card-icon svg {
  width: 22px; height: 22px;
  stroke: var(--clr-primary);
  fill: none;
  stroke-width: 2;
  stroke-linecap: round;
  stroke-linejoin: round;
}
.support-card h3 {
  font-family: var(--ff-head);
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--clr-text-dark);
  margin: 0;
  line-height: 1.30;
}
.support-card p {
  font-family: var(--ff-body);
  font-size: var(--font-size-base);
  color: var(--clr-text-body);
  line-height: 1.65;
  margin: 0;
}
@media(max-width:768px) {
  .support-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
}

/* ══ HODNOTY – CITÁTOVÁ SEKCE ══ */
.values-section {
  background: var(--clr-primary-soft);
  padding: 88px 0;
}
.values-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 28px;
  margin-top: 52px;
}
.value-card {
  background: #fff;
  border-radius: var(--radius-card);
  padding: 36px 32px;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 16px;
  box-shadow: var(--shadow-card);
}
.value-card-quote {
  font-family: var(--ff-head);
  font-size: 3rem;
  line-height: 1;
  color: var(--clr-primary);
  opacity: 0.35;
  margin: 0;
  display: block;
}
.value-card-text {
  font-family: var(--ff-head);
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  font-style: italic;
  color: var(--clr-text-dark);
  line-height: 1.60;
  margin: 0;
}
.value-card-source {
  font-family: var(--ff-body);
  font-size: var(--font-size-caption);
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--clr-text-muted);
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: .07em;
}
@media(max-width:768px) {
  .values-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
}

/* ══ CTA ══ */
.cta-section {
  background: #EDE8E3;
  padding: 88px 0;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.cta-section::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  width: 360px; height: 360px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: rgba(155,66,73,0.08);
  top: -100px; right: -60px;
  pointer-events: none;
}
.cta-section::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  width: 220px; height: 220px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: rgba(155,66,73,0.05);
  bottom: -60px; left: -40px;
  pointer-events: none;
}
.cta-inner {
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
  text-align: center;
  max-width: 640px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}
.cta-inner .section-label { color: var(--clr-primary); }
.cta-inner h2 {
  font-family: var(--ff-head);
  font-size: var(--font-size-h2);
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--clr-primary);
  line-height: 1.20;
  margin: 0 0 16px;
}
.cta-inner p {
  font-family: var(--ff-body);
  font-size: var(--font-size-base);
  color: var(--clr-text-body);
  line-height: 1.70;
  margin: 0 0 32px;
}
.cta-btn-wrap {
  display: flex;
  gap: 12px;
  justify-content: center;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}
.btn-primary {
  display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
  background: var(--clr-primary); color: #fff;
  border: 2px solid var(--clr-primary);
  font-family: var(--ff-body); font-size: var(--font-size-ui); font-weight: 600;
  padding: 13px 28px; border-radius: var(--radius-btn);
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: background .2s, border-color .2s;
}
.btn-primary:hover { background: var(--clr-primary-hover); border-color: var(--clr-primary-hover); }
.btn-secondary {
  display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
  background: transparent; color: var(--clr-primary);
  border: 2px solid var(--clr-primary);
  font-family: var(--ff-body); font-size: var(--font-size-ui); font-weight: 600;
  padding: 13px 28px; border-radius: var(--radius-btn);
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: background .2s;
}
.btn-secondary:hover { background: var(--clr-primary-soft); }
@media(max-width:480px) {
  .cta-inner h2 { font-size: var(--font-size-h2-mob); }
  .cta-btn-wrap { flex-direction: column; align-items: center; }
}

/* ══ RELATED KARTY ══ */
.related-d-section { background: var(--clr-surface); padding: 72px 0; }
.related-d-section h2 { font-family: var(--ff-head); font-size: var(--font-size-h2); font-weight: 700; color: var(--clr-primary); margin: 0 0 8px; }
.related-d-label { font-family: var(--ff-body); font-size: var(--font-size-label); font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: .08em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--clr-primary); display: block; margin-bottom: 12px; }
.related-d-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4,1fr); gap: 20px; margin-top: 36px; }
.related-d-card { background: #fff; border-radius: var(--radius-card); box-shadow: var(--shadow-card); padding: 28px 24px; text-decoration: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; border-top: 3px solid var(--clr-border); transition: box-shadow .22s, transform .22s, border-top-color .22s; color: inherit; }
.related-d-card:hover { box-shadow: var(--shadow-hover); transform: translateY(-4px); border-top-color: var(--clr-primary); }
.related-d-card-label { font-family: var(--ff-body); font-size: var(--font-size-label); font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: .07em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--clr-text-muted); }
.related-d-card-title { font-family: var(--ff-head); font-size: var(--font-size-subhead); font-weight: 600; color: var(--clr-text-dark); line-height: 1.35; }
.related-d-card-desc { font-family: var(--ff-body); font-size: var(--font-size-base); color: var(--clr-text-muted); line-height: 1.55; flex: 1; }
.related-d-card-arrow { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; font-family: var(--ff-body); font-size: var(--font-size-caption); font-weight: 600; color: var(--clr-primary); margin-top: 4px; transition: gap .18s; }
.related-d-card:hover .related-d-card-arrow { gap: 10px; }
.related-d-card-arrow svg { width: 16px; height: 16px; flex-shrink: 0; stroke: currentColor; fill: none; stroke-width: 2; stroke-linecap: round; stroke-linejoin: round; }
@media(max-width:1024px) { .related-d-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2,1fr); } }
@media(max-width:768px) { .related-d-section { padding: 56px 0; } .related-d-section h2 { font-size: var(--font-size-h2-mob); } }
@media(max-width:480px) { .related-d-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
</style>

<!-- ══ HERO ══ -->
<section class="tym-hero">
  <div class="tym-hero-inner">
    <span class="tym-hero-kicker">Tým Domova Turovice</span>
    <h1>Lidé, kteří <em>o vás pečují</em></h1>
    <p class="tym-hero-perex">Za každodenní péčí v Domově Turovice stojí konkrétní lidé. Zdravotní sestry, pečovatelky, sociální pracovnice a aktivizační pracovníci – tým, který zajišťuje péči o seniory 24 hodin denně, 365 dní v roce.</p>
    <div class="hero-btn-wrap">
      <a href="#tym-obsah" class="hero-btn-primary">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="16" height="16" stroke="currentColor" fill="none" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"/><polyline points="19 12 12 19 5 12"/></svg>
        Poznat náš tým
      </a>
      <a href="/kontakt" class="hero-btn-secondary">Napsat nám</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══ STAT STRIP ══ -->
<section class="stat-strip">
  <div class="stat-strip-inner">
    <div>
      <span class="stat-item-num">22 let</span>
      <span class="stat-item-label">praxe ředitelky v sociálních&nbsp;službách</span>
    </div>
    <div>
      <span class="stat-item-num">104</span>
      <span class="stat-item-label">míst pro klienty v péči zkušeného&nbsp;týmu</span>
    </div>
    <div>
      <span class="stat-item-num">24/7</span>
      <span class="stat-item-label">ošetřovatelská péče každý den v&nbsp;roce</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══ VEDENÍ ══ -->
<section class="vedeni-section" id="tym-obsah">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-intro">
      <span class="section-label">Vedení domova</span>
      <h2>Kdo stojí za Domovem Turovice</h2>
      <p>Domov řídí ředitelka s dvaceti dvěma lety přímé práce s klienty. Není to manažerka za stolem – je to odbornice, která zná péči o seniory zevnitř.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="vedeni-card">
      <div class="vedeni-photo">
        <div class="vedeni-photo-placeholder">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="8" r="4"/><path d="M4 20c0-4 3.6-7 8-7s8 3 8 7"/></svg>
          Fotografie<br>ředitelky<br>(600×800 px)
        </div>
        <span class="vedeni-badge">Ředitelka</span>
